            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-Hd1e108">Rubrica 7</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De riduculis et vtrapelia</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>
      ¶ De riduculis et eutrapelia. Rubrica. 7.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="68"/> <ref>CRonica de nugis philosophorum
      <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>capitulo 6. scilicet de biante</ref>
      <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-Qd1e127">Bias vnus de septem sapiententibus
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>nauigans cum quibusdam impiis
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>periclitante naui ac illis deos inuocantibus
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>silete inquit ne sentiant nos hic nauigantes.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-d1e137">
               <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>
       ¶ <ref>Aristoteles rethoricorum libro i. capitulo 20.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-Qd1e141">Omnis remissio
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>et risus delectabilium est. Necesse est risibi
        <lb ed="#V" n="76" break="no"/>lia delectabilia esse: et homines: et verba: et
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>opera.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-d1e152"> 
       / <ref>Libro 2. capitulo 16.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-Qd1e154">Iuuenes sunt amato
        <lb ed="#V" n="78" break="no"/>res risus: propter quod et eutrapelli. eutrape
        <lb ed="#V" n="79" break="no"/>lia autem erudita contumelia est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-d1e162"> 
         / <ref>Idem
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>ethicorum: libro 4. capitulo 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-Qd1e164">Qui neque ipsi dicunt ali
        <lb ed="#V" n="81" break="no"/>quod ridiculum et dicentibus molesti sunt
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>aggrestes et duri videntur esse: moderate autem
        <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>ludentes eutrapelli appellantur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-d1e176">
               <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>
       ¶ <ref>Tullius de oratore: libro 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-Qd1e180">Hec ridentur vel
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>sola vel maxime que notant vel signant tur
        <lb ed="#V" n="86" break="no"/>pitudinem aliquam non turpiter. Hylaritas
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>beniuolentiam conciliat ei per quem excitata
        <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>est. Materies ridiculorum omnis est in his vitiis
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>que sunt in vitis hominum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-d1e194">
               <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>
       ¶ <ref>Ualerius maximus: libro i. de neglecta reli <!--250.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="106-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1" break="no"/>gione.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-Qd1e198">Dionysius genitus siracusis detracta
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>ioui <sic>olypio</sic> magis ponderis aureo amitulo
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>quo eum tyrannus hirte manubiis cartha
        <lb ed="#V" n="4" break="no"/>ginensium ornauerat: iniectoque laneo palio
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>dixit: estate graue esse aureum amitolum.
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>hyeme frigidum: laneum autem ad vtrumque
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>anni tempus aptius.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-d1e223"> 
         / <ref>Idem</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-Qd1e225">dionysius vi
        <lb ed="#V" n="8" break="no"/>tas aureas et pateras et coronas que simul
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>acrorum porrectis manibus sustinebantur
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>tollebat et eas se accipere non auferre dice
        <lb ed="#V" n="11" break="no"/>bat: per quem stultum esse argumentando a
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>quibuscunque bona precamur: ab his porri
        <lb ed="#V" n="13" break="no"/>gentibus nolle sumere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-d1e242"> 
          / <ref>Libro 3. titulo de fiducia
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>sui:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d83992-Qd1e244">Spartanus quidam referente quodam
        <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>sagittis persarum solem obscurari solere:
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>bene narras inquit. in vmbra enim proeliabimur.</quote>
            </p>
